  "summary": "'YOU DESERVE MORE' headline: Agenda font (email fallback Nunito Sans ExtraBold), ALL CAPS, brand Gold/Sunshine or Blue colors; 'D' and 'M' at 40% tint; hero stacks three lines, left-aligned."
